向量網路分析儀









Anritsu offers a variety of vector network analyzers (VNAs) to suit your application. Choose from an RF VNA to a Broadband VNA, from a Premium VNA with the highest performance and no compromises to a Value VNA that offers solid performance with suitable measurement speeds for an R&D environment. No matter what your application, Anritsu has your VNA needs covered. Choose with confidence from the pioneers in VNA measurements, introducing the Wiltron 310 Impedance Meter in 1965, and introducing the first broadband VNA, spanning 40 MHz to 65 GHz, in 1999.













